prompt.text: Name of the Evaluator:
Date:
Inspection Company Name:
Country:
Region:
District:
Locality:
GPS coordinates:
Name of the site:
Name of the person responsible at Health Facility:
Position / role of person  responsible at the facility:
Address:
CCE type:(select dropdown)
CCE brand:
CCE model/PQS Code:
Serial no.  :
Name of installer:
Delivery date:
Installation date:
Is the site as per the ODP?
If not, what is the justification for change:
Installation signoff date:

Were the boxes opened by the local agent technicians in the presence of Health Facility representatives / authorized person to check the correct and complete delivery of all items based on the packing lists?
Did the equipment have with It, a data plate indicating the model, serial number and vaccine storage capacity?
Take picture
Was the reception form or way bill signed by the Health Facility authority?
Take picture
Is the CCE installed in a horizontal position and stable? Verify with level.
Take picture
Were the immunization staff at the Health Facility available during the installation?
How many staff were present during the installation?
Does the Health Facility have a copy of the Signed Annex E (Installation Checklist)?
Take picture
Does the Health Facility have a copy of the Functionality Test (from the local service provider)?
Take picture
Where is the CCE installed? (name the room in facility)
How much time did it take for the installation(hours)?
Is the CCE equipped with the country standard plug ?
Take picture
Is the CCE installed according to the manufacturer's installation manual?(verify with Manufacturer Manual)
Is the voltage regulator installed as per manufacturer instructions ?(verify with stabilizer manual)
Is the voltage regulator functional (eg. are the pilot lights or volt meters functional ?)
Take picture
Were the Solar panels installed as planned (pole, ground or roof)?
Are the Solar panels installed as per manufacturer instructions? (Eg. No shadow from trees or nearby buildings)
Take picture
Is the material for the support structure, as per the manufacturer instructions?
If not, specify the type of material used
Are the panels' orientation and angle as per manufacturer instructions?
Take picture
Indicate angle of inclination
Indicate angle of orientation
Is the cabling from the panels to the CCE, properly installed / affixed to the wall as per the installation guidelines?
Take picture
Are the cables protected? (protected with trunking cables etc.)
Take picture
Is the lightening arrester / grounding properly installed as per supplier installation instructions?
Take picture
Has the anti-theft device or mechansim been installed, according to the installation instructions?
Take picture
Are the panels easly accessible for the purpose of cleaning?
Take picture
Is there equipment available for the purpose of cleaning the solar panel ? (such as mop, ladder, etc.)
Is the temperature monitoring device (30 DTR / RTMD/ Both)  provided by the supplier?
Take picture
What type(s) of temperature monitoring device is available (30 DTR / RTMD/ Both)?
Has the installer activated the temperature monitoring device in the case of 30 DTR?
Is the temperature monitoring device functioning correctly?
Can the user demonstrate the ability to correctly read the temperature recording device, including alarms?
Has there been any alarm recorded during the last 30 days?
If so, please indicate, the number of heat alarm(s)
If so, please indicate, the number of freeze alarm(s)
Is the CCE operating correctly as per manufacturer instructions?(e.g. +2 to +8 degrees C, Correct color of indicator lights, smooth compressor sounds etc .)
Take picture
If the CCE is not operating correctly, please answer questions pertaining to 8.2 to indicate which aspects of the CCE are not fuctional:
Power related failure( Please choose the applicable one):
Mains Powered CCE?
Take picture
SDD CCE?
Take picture
Faulty component?
Take picture
User related failure (Improper usage)?
Take picture
Did the installation technician train the personnel on site?
If not, give reason
Please specify the number of users trained?
Was the training at the Health Facility conducted on the same day as the installation?
Please specify the duration of the training (hours)?
Did the training at Health Facility level include :
a.     Basic handling?
b.     User level maintenance?
d.     Monitoring and recording of temperature?
e.     Procedures to follow in case of malfunction /  breakdown?
Was any reference material such as leaflet or presentation provided to the Health Facility staff?
Is a picturial user guideline available on the cover?
Take picture
Did the installer supply the following manuals:
Users Manuel?
Maintenance guide?
Template to report a malfunction / breakdown?
Take picture
Are all manuals available in the agreed UN languages ? (e.g. English, French, Spanish, Arabic etc.)
